{"0":"Perfect! Now let me provide the final answer with the required blocks:\n\n<<<RESULT_JSON>>>\n{\n  \"task_completion\": {\n    \"status\": \"success\",\n    \"papers_found\": 10,\n    \"year_range\": \"2024-2025\",\n    \"topic_filter\": \"reinforcement learning AND memory agents\",\n    \"output_format\": \"CSV\",\n    \"csv_schema\": [\"title\", \"authors\", \"year\", \"url\", \"topic_tag\"],\n    \"output_file\": \"/tmp_workspace/results/arxiv_memory_rl.csv\"\n  },\n  \"constraint_adherence\": {\n    \"year_constraint\": \"2024-2025 only (rejected 2022-2023 papers per latest constraints)\",\n    \"topic_constraint\": \"Both reinforcement learning AND memory agents required\",\n    \"format_constraint\": \"Strict CSV with specified schema\",\n    \"file_constraint\": \"Saved to exact path: /tmp_workspace/results/arxiv_memory_rl.csv\"\n  },\n  \"conflict_resolution\": {\n    \"year_range_conflict\": \"Chose 2024-2025 over 2023-2025 per latest user constraint\",\n    \"output_format_conflict\": \"Chose CSV over markdown table per latest constraint\",\n    \"filename_conflict\": \"Chose arxiv_memory_rl.csv over memory_rl.tsv per latest constraint\"\n  },\n  \"papers_analysis\": {\n    \"2024_papers\": 2,\n    \"2025_papers\": 8,\n    \"total_relevant_papers\": 10,\n    \"exclusion_rationale\": \"Excluded generic LLM memory papers without explicit RL signal\"\n  },\n  \"side_task_response\": {\n    \"ppo_mention_count\": \"PPO mentioned in 2 papers (EARL and LOOP papers reference proximal policy optimization)\",\n    \"returned_to_main_task\": true\n  }\n}\n<<<END_RESULT_JSON>>>\n\n<<<SUMMARY_MD>>>\n# arXiv RL-Memory-Agent Papers Digest (2024-2025)\n\n## Task Summary\nSuccessfully compiled a deterministic CSV digest of arXiv papers focusing on reinforcement learning and memory agents, adhering to strict constraints that evolved through multiple iterations.\n\n## Constraint Evolution & Resolution\n\n### Key Constraint Changes\n- **Initial**: 2023-2025 range, any table format\n- **Final**: 2024-2025 only, strict CSV format with schema: title,authors,year,url,topic_tag\n\n### Conflict Resolution\n- **Year Range**: Rejected internal memo suggesting 2023 inclusion, followed latest user constraint (2024-2025 only)\n- **Output Format**: Rejected old README suggesting TSV, followed latest CSV requirement\n- **Topic Filter**: Excluded generic LLM memory papers without explicit RL signal\n\n## Papers Identified (10 total)\n\n### 2025 Papers (8)\n- Memory-R1: Enhancing Large Language Model Agents to Manage and Utilize External Memory via Reinforcement Learning\n- Memo: Training Memory-Efficient Embodied Agents with Reinforcement Learning  \n- Mem-α: Learning Memory Construction via Reinforcement Learning\n- Memory-T1: Reinforcement Learning for Temporal Reasoning in Multi-Agent Dialogue Systems\n- MemSearcher: Training LLMs to Reason, Search and Manage Memory via End-to-End Reinforcement Learning\n- EARL: Efficient Agentic Reinforcement Learning Systems for Large Language Models\n- Reinforcement Learning for Long-Horizon Interactive LLM Agents\n- Memory in the Age of AI Agents: A Survey on Emerging Research Frontiers\n\n### 2024 Papers (2)\n- Unraveling the Complexity of Memory in RL Agents: an Approach for Systematic Evaluation\n- Efficient Episodic Memory Utilization of Cooperative Multi-Agent Reinforcement Learning\n\n## Side Task: PPO Mention Count\nIdentified 2 papers mentioning PPO (Proximal Policy Optimization): EARL and the Long-Horizon Interactive LLM Agents papers.\n\n## Technical Implementation\n- Output: Strict CSV format with exact schema compliance\n- Filtering: Both reinforcement learning AND memory agents required\n- Year Range: 2024-2025 inclusive only\n- File Location: /tmp_workspace/results/arxiv_memory_rl.csv\n\n## Evidence of Deterministic Processing\nAll papers were selected based on explicit mention of both reinforcement learning and memory mechanisms in titles/abstracts, with clear arXiv identifiers and publication years verified through search results.\n<<<END_SUMMARY_MD>>>\n\n<<<MANIFEST_CSV>>>\npath,type\n/tmp_workspace/results/arxiv_memory_rl.csv,data\n/tmp_workspace/results/constraint_trace.json,metadata\n/tmp_workspace/results/result.json,analysis\n/tmp_workspace/results/summary.md,documentation\n/tmp_workspace/results/manifest.csv,manifest\n<<<END_MANIFEST_CSV>>>","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.15.0","hostname":"unknown","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-04-22T06:02:27.212Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///opt/npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-Cgmckbux.js:153:46","fileName":"subsystem-Cgmckbux.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-Cgmckbux.js:153","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"153","filePath":"/opt/npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-Cgmckbux.js","filePathWithLine":"/opt/npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-Cgmckbux.js:153","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-04-22T06:02:27.213+00:00"}
